##RUN PROJECT IN FLASK 

### STEPS RUN app in local

---cd folder the project

----Set up a virtual environment in a directory named venv with the command:

  --Windows c/s path:
      python -m venv venv 

Activate the virtual environment:

  --Windows c/s path:
      venv\Scripts\Activate

Install the requirements.txt with the command:
    pip install -r requirements.txt


Move to folder path database:

1. In the schema.sql file add SQL to create the tables or new fields 
2. In the path in databse execute  --- python init_db.py

Start Flask with the command:

1. flask run
2. Go the ip http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/v1/doc